{"tid":1729040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府都宣布聽日停課助攻 如果你仲返工 係完全浪費左隻好牌","createTime":"2019-11-17T06:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T06:14:55.000Z","uid":30862,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c094ec9e74af8e2eca18c39a7822a02580f07a79","tid":1729040,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"不戰而屈人之兵，善之善者也<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地目的係以全港三罷去逼使政府答應五大訴求(最少)<br />\n依家三個達成條件之一 罷課 已經ok左喇喎<br />\n<br />\n加埋罷工已有三分二<br />\n咁靚既牌面 香港人爭氣啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連黎明都少左一大部分阻力！！！<br />\n邊個話自己黃/想贏既人 而聽日繼續返工 繼續玩和你lunch彈出又彈入 想食兩家茶禮既人<br />\n我只希望你地諗清楚 你地最終想得到既<br />\n<br />\n係短暫既生存 <br />\n定係重光之後既生活<br />\n<br />\n有仔女既 應該要留係屋企陪佢地 溝通下<br />\n冇仔女既 唔該做你應該要做既野<br />\n<br />\n香港人愈來愈接近勝利架啦！<br />\n唔好放棄！更加要把握好時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(或者有新方法贏既話 歡迎討論)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我知點做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：繼續返工繼續嬲嬲救港"},{"pid":"6373dae05ad84963811bc109620ebbc2273c2019","tid":1729040,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:02:11.000Z","msg":"唔該大家諗清楚<br />\n要做既野係咩<br />\n<br />\n我相信大家既智慧"},{"pid":"14fe825c03d85edfbd6fa252a54f24818f678df9","tid":1729040,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:03:24.000Z","msg":"勝利條件：1/3已經"},{"pid":"ab2378720d096fcf57aba844f7665414b51a41fc","tid":1729040,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84cdc63348e1b82b4b228d601f921c783af71f18","tid":1729040,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"6798ebadb4bf06e886cf86231eba70d56b51f49d","tid":1729040,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:04:53.000Z","ms